  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Founded in 2002, GEM Co., Ltd. (GEM, the Company) is a leading waste recycler and manufacturer of lithium-based battery materials in China. The proposed investment is a RMB 500 million (approximately US$76 million equivalent) A Loan to support the Companys construction of new recycling facilities in Hubei Province, a frontier region of China (the Project).</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Project-level: (i) increase recycling capacities and promote circular economy; and (ii) create employment opportunities and economic linkages. 
Market creation: enhance integration of battery recycling practices.</narrative>
